  "detailed_description": "Dive into the world of Junkcity Factory, a dynamic simulation game where industry meets creativity. With nearly 300 unique items and 29 powerful machines at your disposal, you'll transform scrap materials into valuable products in a bustling factory environment.<br><br>Set within a vibrant, medium-sized city, Junkcity Factory challenges you to collect hundreds of different scraps, manage 33 workers, and oversee their wages while running a fully interactive factory. Optimize each worker's efficiency to maximize your profits as you watch every item in your inventory interact with real-world physics—whether they drop, stack, or move along the production line.<br><br>Your factory is the heart of your operations, where every process must be fine-tuned for success. From recycling to manufacturing, and from managing your workforce to selling your products in the Junkcity Store, every choice you make will impact your bottom line.<br><br><br><br>Will you rise to become the ultimate industrial magnate?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213220/extras/c043353d3b8068c32674d1ae9ef3677f.poster.avif?t=1734335782\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213220/extras/c043353d3b8068c32674d1ae9ef3677f.webm?t=1734335782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213220/extras/c043353d3b8068c32674d1ae9ef3677f.mp4?t=1734335782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213220/extras/b6af05d8b8e414e07a3b92da3f35fcf8.poster.avif?t=1734335782\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213220/extras/b6af05d8b8e414e07a3b92da3f35fcf8.webm?t=1734335782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213220/extras/b6af05d8b8e414e07a3b92da3f35fcf8.mp4?t=1734335782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213220/extras/2f3f32efc8e7f6c1a110fa060922b20c.poster.avif?t=1734335782\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213220/extras/2f3f32efc8e7f6c1a110fa060922b20c.webm?t=1734335782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213220/extras/2f3f32efc8e7f6c1a110fa060922b20c.mp4?t=1734335782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213220/extras/06f3732c104533a851471f0e1d2583c6.poster.avif?t=1734335782\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213220/extras/06f3732c104533a851471f0e1d2583c6.webm?t=1734335782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213220/extras/06f3732c104533a851471f0e1d2583c6.mp4?t=1734335782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213220/extras/e463b92bf290bd4b3b8015fb5b02ae20.poster.avif?t=1734335782\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213220/extras/e463b92bf290bd4b3b8015fb5b02ae20.webm?t=1734335782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3213220/extras/e463b92bf290bd4b3b8015fb5b02ae20.mp4?t=1734335782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Features:<br><br>Collect and recycle hundreds of unique scrap items.<br>Manage a large-scale factory with 29 specialized machines and 33 workers.<br>Oversee your workers, optimize their efficiency, and manage their wages.<br>Experience realistic physics that bring every item to life.<br>Sell your products at the Junkcity Store and influence the city’s economy.",
